      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      139.54,
      543.61,
      153.58
    ],
    "text": "signatory to the Covenant and the main objective of the Act is to give effect to the",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      161.74,
      543.61,
      175.78
    ],
    "text": "Covenant and in my view the provisions of the Act must be referable to a",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      183.94,
      543.61,
      197.98
    ],
