    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      272.65,
      543.31,
      286.69
    ],
    "text": "offence under any matter shall have the right of appeal to a higher court against",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      294.73,
      323.0,
      308.77
    ],
    "text": "such conviction and any sentence imposed.",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      316.93,
      543.51,
      330.97
    ],
    "text": "In instances where no right of appeal is conferred by a statute, a party aggrieved,",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      339.13,
      543.53,
      353.17
    ],
    "text": "could invoke the revisionary jurisdiction to have a decision of an original court",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      361.33,
      543.29,
      375.37
    ],
    "text": "reviewed and our courts have always recognized revisionary jurisdiction in such",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      383.41,
      543.47,
      397.45
    ],
    "text": "instances. The provision embodied in Section 4 (2) of the ICCPR Act has now",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      405.61,
      543.44,
      419.65
    ],
    "text": "expanded the scope (of jurisdiction) to appeals in the case of all criminal",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      427.83,
      543.29,
      441.87
    ],
    "text": "offences. While the expansion of the appellate jurisdiction by virtue of section 4",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      450.03,
      543.61,
      464.07
    ],
    "text": "(2) of the ICCPR Act relates exclusively to criminal cases, concomitantly, it must",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      472.11,
      543.48,
      486.15
    ],
    "text": "be stated, that Section 4 (2) of the ICCPR Act has no application whatsoever to",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      494.31,
      139.37,
      508.35
    ],
    "text": "civil cases.",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      516.51,
      543.43,
      530.55
    ],
    "text": "Violation of Section 64 (a) of the Sri Lanka Bureau of Foreign Employment Act",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      538.71,
      543.61,
      552.75
    ],
    "text": "No.21 of 1985 can be visited with penal sanctions and thus falls within the scope",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      560.79,
      543.55,
      574.83
    ],
    "text": "of \u201ccriminal offences under any written law\u201d referred to in Section 4 (2) of the",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      582.99,
      543.29,
      597.03
    ],
