      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      605.22,
      543.21,
      619.26
    ],
    "text": "the right of appeal against a conviction and a sentence imposed for a violation",
    "fonts": [
      "FootlightMTLight"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      627.42,
      543.61,
      641.46
    ],
    "text": "under the Act. Thus, I hold that the Accused-Appellant has a right of appeal",
